headline.main: McCollum Scores 31 in Trail Blazers' 130-116 Win Over Nets
headline.print_headline: McCollum Scores 31 in Trail Blazers' 130-116 Win Over Nets

lead_paragraph: CJ McCollum scored 31 points to lead the Portland Trail Blazers past the Brooklyn Nets 130-116 on Saturday night.
